rasurama and the day Tretayuga started). It is said that spiritual s=\r\nadhana done on Akshaya Tritiya is 1,000 times more effective than a normal =\r\nday. I was excited that the day I picked at random happened to be an auspic=\r\nious day.&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;I mentioned it to Manish. He said, &quot;I knew it was Akshaya =\r\nTritiya even when you mentioned the intention to me&quot;. I asked him why he di=\r\nd not tell that to me then. He curtly remarked, &quot;knowing you were doing thi=\r\ns sadhana on Akshaya Tritiya would not have helped and would have instead d=\r\nistracted you.&quot;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;He was right. As such, I was a little &quot;proud&quot; of the=\r\n sadhana - spending the whole day in japam. There was a bit of\n excitement =\r\nand expectancy that was present as an undercurrent and somewhat distracted =\r\nmy focus on the mantra. Had I known that I was doing it on a day when sadha=\r\nna is supposed to be 1,000 times more effective, that undercurrent of usele=\r\nss excitement would&#39;ve been higher and distracted me even more!&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;Bott=\r\nomline: Thumbrules of all kinds exist. But what really matters is the state=\r\n of your mind. Sometimes, doing a sadhana on an auspicious day can create e=\r\nxcitement and expectancy and distract one. Doing the same sadhana everyday =\r\nand patiently waiting for it to succeed oneday is perhaps a simpler and mor=\r\ne foolproof strategy. My 2 cents..&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;Best regards,&lt;BR&gt;Narasimha&lt;BR&gt;---=\r\n--------- --------- --------- --------- --------- --------- -&lt;BR&gt;Free Jyoti=\r\nsh Software, Free Jyotish Lessons, Jyotish Writings,&lt;BR&gt;&quot;Do It Yourself&quot; ri=\r\ntual manuals for short Homam and Pitri Tarpana:&lt;BR&gt;&lt;A href=3D&quot;http://www.ve=\r\ndicastrologer.org/&quot; rel=3Dnofollow\n target=3D_blank&gt;http://www.VedicAst rol=\r\noger.org&lt;/A&gt;&lt;BR&gt;Films that make a difference: &lt;A href=3D&quot;http://saraswatifi=\r\nlms.org